de range of complex nanoscopic and\ncolloidal systems that was previously inaccessible to lattice-based continuum\nalgorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2016 16:32:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 10:34:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2016 14:34:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-15"}
