alization allows a\nrobust test of whether the apparently isotropic emission in an image is due to\nunresolved point sources or of truly diffuse origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2016 19:58:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2017 21:14:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
