at other\nepochs. We anticipate our study to be a starting point for more effective\ndetermination of the structure effect in VLBI observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Jul 2016 05:09:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-09"}
